  "translations": {
    "en": "As for the right of the benefactor, thank him, mention his kindness, speak well of him, and sincerely supplicate for him before Allah. Then if able, repay him. As for the muezzin's right, know he reminds you of your Lord, calls you to your fortune, and helps you fulfil Allah's obligation. Thank him as you would a benefactor.",
